parameters.message: "Hey man! I'm back! I'm feeling better now! HEY! Are you eating my burguer?"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Oh! Yes!" - I take a big bite just to make sure he believes me. - "It's delicious!"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: In fact, it is really delicious. Puke or no puke, this Burger is awesome.
"Really? Nobody ever tries my dishes..."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Why?"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Dunno. Maybe they think that because I take care of my body, I am a terrible cook."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Well, you are not."
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Thanks!"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "And your body is, indeed, very nice. I wish I could maintain a body like that."
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Th-Thanks man! Hahaha"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: Keisuke seems a little nervous.
"Yours isn't half as bad actually. I like slim built guys."
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: What? Did he just say he likes... guys? Guys like me...?
It's probably just the alcohol speaking.
Still... A guy like him... Into me...
I notice we just made a huge mess in the kitchen and we need to clean this up SOON.
"Umm... Keisuke... we really can't leave all this mess behind"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: "Oh, right!  I gotta take care of the dishes."

parameters.message: "Hey man, whaddya say you help me with this and we'll get it over with before you can say "GUACUM MOLE"! Hahahaha!"
parameters.name: Keisuke

parameters.message: "Hahahahaha!"
parameters.name: Hameru Tabe

parameters.message: We both laugh.
We quickly get to the cleaning. Keisuke does the dishes and I dry them off and put them away.
As I walked to the cabinet I feel a splash on my back...
He he he he...
parameters.name: Keisuke
